details.body:
Annual and monitoring reports providing information and data on the extraction, sales, supply and demand for primary aggregates, as well as information on marine and recycled and secondary aggregates.

2022

  • East of England aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 6.7MB, 102 pages)
  • East Midlands aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022
  • North East aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 1.57 MB, 77 pages)
  • South East aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 2.1MB, 80 pages)
  • South West aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 5.9MB, 92 pages)
  • West Midlands aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 1.11 MB, 49 pages)
  • Yorkshire and Humber aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2022 (PDF, 1.23 MB, 50 pages)

2021

  • East Midlands aggregates working party: annual report 2021 (PDF, 2.8 MB, 71 pages)
  • East of England aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 6.08 MB, 104 pages)
  • North East aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 1.86 MB, 61 pages)
  • North West aggregates working party - annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 827 KB, 51 pages)
  • South East England aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 2.41 MB, 93 pages)
  • South West aggregates working party: annual report 2021 (PDF, 4.9 MB, 89 pages)
  • West Midlands aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 1.2 MB, 48 pages)
  • Yorkshire and Humber aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2021 (PDF, 902 KB, 68 pages)

  • East Midlands aggregates working party: annual report 2020 (PDF, 1.95 MB, 53 pages)
  • East of England aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2020 (PDF, 2.4 MB, 67 pages)
  • North East aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2020 (PDF, 1.69 MB, 46 pages)
  • North West aggregates working party - annual monitoring report 2020 (PDF, 1.19 MB, 47 pages)
  • South East England aggregates working party: annual report 2020
  • South West aggregates working party: annual report 2020 (PDF, 2.5 MB, 58 pages)
  • West Midlands aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2019 and 2020 (PDF, 807 KB, 38 pages)
  • Yorkshire and Humberside aggregates working party: annual monitoring report 2019 and 2020 (PDF, 1.23 MB, 46 pages)

For reports from 2008 to 2019 please see the archived version of this page.
